# GitHub Meta
After the MDX block, append:
- a short SEO-friendly filename like smart-slug.mdx
- a git commit message like: feat: added guide on [topic]

# Writing Quality Rules
- Do not write like a therapist, coach, or lecturer.
- Do not use vague spiritual language.
- Make every paragraph move the reader forward.
- Prefer clarity over cleverness.
- If a sentence can be simpler, make it simpler.

# Final Strict Command
Self-Correction Loop: Before outputting the final response, review your text. If there is any sentence a complete beginner cannot understand, rewrite it to be simpler. Verify all H2s are SEO-optimized. Verify the perspective is First Person. Only output the final, corrected result.`;
      };

